<h2 class="bold font-l">Two Special One-Pounders...</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
When Emi catches sight of Chiho's... rather ample breasts and suffers a bout of A-Cup Angst, it cuts to Maou at work serving a pair of one-pound burgers. Topped with pickles, no less! And then Chiho takes note of Emi's chest, where it then cuts to Maou serving a pair of smaller, flatter burgers. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/VisualInnuendo" class='trope-example-link'>Visual Innuendo</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="y4jfpm" data-video-descrip="Emi's death threats would probably be a lot more effective if she wasn't easily thwarted by a locked door." data-video-title="Emi Threatens Maou" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/y4jfpm_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/y4jfpm.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/FailedAttemptAtDrama" data-video-tropename="Failed Attempt at Drama" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="LightNovel/TheDevilIsAPartTimer" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/y4jfpm.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Emi Threatens Maou</span></p>
</a>
</div>
